  "description": "Transform your combat into a more cinematic and dynamic experience.",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EMTr5QJ.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"100\"><div style=\"border:3px solid #fa0707\"><p style=\"color:#fa0707;font-size:1.7em;text-align:center\"><strong>Third View On Attack</strong></p><p style=\"color:#fff;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>Transform your combat into a more cinematic and dynamic experience. This mod</strong> <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>automatically switches your camera to third person</strong></span> <strong>when you attack a hostile mob, letting you appreciate every slash and showdown from a dramatic view.</strong></p><p style=\"color:#fff;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>Once all nearby enemies are defeated or you move far enough away, the camera transitions back to first person after a short delay. The mod</strong> <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>ignores villagers and wandering traders</strong></span>, <strong>keeping the focus on what truly matters — the battle.</strong></p><p style=\"color:#fa0707;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>Perfect for players who want a more cinematic, dynamic, and immersive Minecraft experience.</strong></p><br><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExaWcwNHBuMm12OG5jYXdjM3U4MXVmcDJzeThrbWR0N28yY2g4N3l6MCZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/7jucVHkRULqyzNChaw/giphy.gif\" alt=\"Third View On Attack GIF\"></p></div><p><br></p><div style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/4gytaRTKuc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bBpJOKO.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"> </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_d_4.v_1_d_/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YHadOI4.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"> </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&